arameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"06d9d904-5f77-4a3a-b667-e70e58ff6014","name":"failedNode","value":"={{ $json.error?.node?.name || 'unknown' }}","type":"string"},{"id":"2e030d5d-9be3-4dd8-8387-20ec9a4139fe","name":"errorMessage","value":"={{ $json.error?.message || JSON.stringify($json).slice(0,200) }}","type":"string"},{"id":"696a920c-c13b-42e7-931f-e9bc1b22bffa","name":"workflow","value":"={{ $workflow.name }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[4509,1420],"id":"49a181d0-4ad5-4d81-b092-84743222a6b5","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"subject":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage ","bodyContent":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","toRecipients":"={{ $json.email || 'ops@company.com' }}","additionalFields":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.microsoftOutlook","typeVersion":2,"position":[4833,1420],"id":"69b58dbf-685c-442f-a915-5f146ce43c03","name":"Escalate Failure to Outlook","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Receive Inbound Webhook\n\nEntry point: listens for POST calls on `/wf06657-document`. Use the TEST url while building, switch callers to the PRODUCTION url after publishing.\n\nNext: Collect Raw Text","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"b3b53232-433f-8324-6eb8-3506145f061d","name":"Note: Receive Inbound Webhook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Collect Raw Text\n\nShapes the item: writes `content`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Extract Structured Fields","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"03a29619-16a7-6174-3737-52bfff28d849","name":"Note: Collect Raw Text"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Extract Structured Fields\n\nPulls structured fields (docId, title, sourceUrl) out of free text using a strict extraction prompt.\n\nPorts: ①→ All Required Fields Found? · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"6f07c26c-f42b-0f7e-ee45-6e892f326bfa","name":"Note: Extract Structured Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### OpenRouter Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Extract Structured Fields** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 OpenRouter API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[561,1090],"id":"66915605-afb6-a4b5-1b32-319a24d039c2","name":"Note: OpenRouter Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### All Required Fields Found?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.output?.docId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Upsert into Airtable · ②→ Queue for Manual Review","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[885,520],"id":"554d79b1-db48-7298-3dca-e5b6ae56cd96","name":"Note: All Required Fields Found?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Upsert into Airtable\n\nairtable — `upsert` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Review Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1209,280],"id":"7469c8d6-6183-473d-281d-c41a5d5f9bf8","name":"Note: Upsert into Airtable"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Queue for Manual Review\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Review Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1533,880],"id":"97656dd3-a52c-023f-8ded-cb595b3b5fc9","name":"Note: Queue for Manual Review"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Review Paths\n\nRejoins 2 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2181,520],"id":"39a2bf01-93c1-f002-6cbc-f67d24f8d656","name":"Note: Merge Review Paths"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 100 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3153,520],"id":"ea86d017-f483-3aed-9740-bc9b177d04e9","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3477,520],"id":"209f5c5e-e882-832d-fe49-928383c4cca7","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Sort Documents Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,520],"id":"ecf49471-fc0d-0b2a-a894-0c9a012f0fc6","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Documents Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4125,520],"id":"1c8de5f6-db7d-c0a8-178d-e1eb5fcae652","name":"Note: Sort Documents Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Airtable)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4449,520],"id":"d1e2c963-f26f-1e96-bf55-773752a6ab75","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Airtable)\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Outlook · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4773,520],"id":"0a5cc715-441d-fe43-4b02-d7d5ba6d463d","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Airtable)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Outlook\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5097,520],"id":"f1ab3c46-76fd-9066-0e29-0bb2e1e5302f","name":"Note: Send Summary to Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Outlook","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4449,1540],"id":"ab77a9f6-b559-9fe2-253d-de05a34812f2","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Outlook\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4773,1540],"id":"28e9ed7e-184c-f0db-7be1-56b53e15b873","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Outlook"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Summarize meeting notes with Airtable and Outlook\n\n**Pattern:** AI Summarize & Route · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nSummarize meeting notes with Airtable and Outlook. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual document search is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Collect Raw Text → Extract Structured Fields → All Required Fields Found? → Upsert into Airtable → Merge Review Paths → Cap Batch Volume → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai summarize & route without manual effort\n- Anyone automating document search in ai\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Airtable PAT; Microsoft OAuth2; OpenRouter API key; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"bec7fcbf-9623-f24c-e7b0-8e51b20d776d","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"0871c189-efa8-55c3-1bfe-f038989d790a","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"26dcd54d-3691-5559-2da6-c691a2d23224","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"3588e828-a3e3-42a9-d225-8ee4a4090f9b","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your document search process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-260],"id":"bc98c4c3-db27-877e-249a-adbc3144c2e9","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Collect Raw Text","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Collect Raw Text":{"main":[[{"node":"Extract Structured Fields","type":"main","index":0}]]},"OpenRouter Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Extract Structured Fields","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Extract Structured Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"All Required Fields Found?","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"All Required Fields Found?":{"main":[[{"node":"Upsert into Airtable","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Queue for Manual Review","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Upsert into Airtable":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Review Paths","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Queue for Manual Review":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Review Paths","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Merge Review Paths":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Documents Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Documents Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Airtable)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Airtable)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Outlook","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Outlook","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Outlook":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"3296274d-a529-42e5-acf5-50f95b51c7a0","id":"FDX06657"}